snippet.title: Iron Seed gameplay (PC Game, 1994)
snippet.description:
Introduction and gameplay for Iron Seed, Dos PC game produced by Channel 7 in 1994 - http://www.squakenet.com/download/iron-seed/7008/
Choosing a crew and exploring the interface in this complex sci-fi adventure.
Played through Dosbox emulation platform.
Recorded with original sound.
